comment: /**  * Copies all of the mappings from the given map into the state.  *  * @param map The mappings to be stored in this state  *  * @throws Exception Thrown if the system cannot access the state.  */

comment: /**  * Deletes the mapping of the given key.  *  * @param key The key of the mapping  *  * @throws Exception Thrown if the system cannot access the state.  */
code: /**  * Deletes the mapping of the given key.  *  * @param key The key of the mapping  *  * @throws Exception Thrown if the system cannot access the state.  */ void remove(K key) throws Exception.
